thread.title: BRIEF-Tactile Systems Technology Q4 Earnings Per Share $0.12

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Tactile Systems Technology Q4 Earnings Per Share $0.12
text:
Feb 26 (Reuters) - Tactile Systems Technology Inc:
* TACTILE SYSTEMS TECHNOLOGY, INC. REPORTS FOURTH QUARTER AND FULL YEAR 2017 FINANCIAL RESULTS; INTRODUCES 2018 OUTLOOK
* Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.12 * Q4 REVENUE $34.9 MILLION * SEES FY 2018 REVENUE UP 20 TO 22 PERCENT * SEES FY 2018 REVENUE $131 MILLION TO $133 MILLION * Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.13, REVENUE VIEW $33.9 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* FY2018 REVENUE VIEW $131.3 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
